These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, march, april, december, october
There are 5 different nationalities: brazilian, british, chinese, pakistani, russian
The people have 5 different jobs:  dressmaker, social-worker, entrepreneur, software-developer, engineer
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, hip-hop, blues, techno, rock
 1. the fan of blues is on the left of the engineer##1
 2. the fan of rock is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the brazilian##1
 4. the fan of house is on the right of the chinese##1
 5. the social-worker is the pakistani##1
 6. the british is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the dressmaker is on the left of the fan of techno##1
 8. the british is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the british##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the fan of house##1
11. the social-worker is the fan of house##1
12. the entrepreneur is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Birthday         | march  | january    | december | april    | october  |
| Nationality   | british  | brazilian | chinese | pakistani | russian  |
| Job           | dressmaker     | engineer     | software-developer  | social-worker   | entrepreneur    |
| Music-Genre         | blues | techno    | hip-hop | house  | rock |

