.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, cucumber, kiwi, lettuce, watermelon
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, fanta, hot-chocolate, mirinda
There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, aquamarine, azure, emerald, grey
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, sunflower, daisy, tulip, aconite
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 2. the person who growsdaisy is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 3. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 4. the person who likes azure is on the far left##1
 5. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is the person who likes azure##1
 9. the person who growstulip is the person eating kiwi##1
10. the person eating cucumber is in the middle##1
11. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
12. the person eating kiwi is the person drinking 7up##1
13. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Food          | kiwi        | watermelon | cucumber     | lettuce      | artichoke  |
| Beverage           | 7up   | fanta | mirinda    | hot-chocolate | soy-milk |
| Color   | azure | emerald     | grey | blue    | aquamarine  |
| Flower   | tulip     | sunflower | bellflower    | aconite      | daisy    |

