.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, davidoff, old-henry, ritmeester, tiparillo
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, reading, traveling, writing
5 different games are played: go, backgammon, monopoly, domino, bridge
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: comedy, western, fantasy, adventure, zombie
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the person playing go is in the middle##1
 4. the davidoff-smoker is in the middle##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
 7. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 9. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
11. the person playing monopoly is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
12. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
13. the ritmeester-smoker is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Cigar      | ritmeester          | old-henry  | davidoff       | swisher     | tiparillo      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | writing | traveling  | reading   | cooking    |
| Game   | backgammon        | bridge | go | domino    | monopoly   |
| Movie-Genre     | comedy   | fantasy | zombie      | western | adventure |

