.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: tulip, zinnia, azalea, sunflower, marigold
House: tower, futuristic, art-deco, gothic-revival, wooden
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, gospel, indie, pop, techno
There are 5 different nationalities: american, mexican, nigerian, pakistani, russian
 1. the futuristic house is on the left of the fan of country##1
 2. the tower house is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 3. the fan of gospel is the futuristic house##1
 4. the fan of country is the tower house##1
 5. the art-deco house is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 6. the nigerian is on the right of the tower house##1
 7. the mexican is on the right of the wooden house##1
 8. the russian is in the middle##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is the fan of indie##1
11. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
12. the american is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Flower          | sunflower        | tulip       | azalea | zinnia   | marigold  |
| House   | wooden | art-deco | futuristic | tower   | gothic-revival |
| Music-Genre   | pop         | techno     | gospel | country | indie     |
| Nationality     | american        | mexican        | russian    | pakistani    | nigerian      |

