.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-5::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower, azalea, rose, daisy
There are 5 different nationalities: colombian, turkish, french, british, dutch
The people use 5 different means of transport: ship, bus, van, scooter, subway
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: parkour, rowing, sailing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person driving the bus is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the french##1
 3. the dutch is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 4. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 6. the colombian is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person driving the ship is on the right of the british##1
 8. the person driving the subway is in the middle##1
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
10. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
11. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person driving the van##1
12. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
| Flower          | balloon-flower    | daisy  | azalea | bellflower    | rose      |
| Nationality           | dutch | french | colombian  | british | turkish |
| Transport   | van           | bus      | subway      | scooter        | ship     |
| Sport         | rowing         | sailing  | parkour   | skiing       | water-polo  |

