.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, rock, classical, metal, ambient
There are 5 different favourite colors: orange, fuchsia, chestnut, azure, coral
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, alhambra, bongani, swisher, prince
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, ice-hockey, lacrosse, weightlifting
 1. the person who likes orange is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 2. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 3. the siglo-smoker is on the far right##1
 4. the person who likes azure is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 7. the person who likes azure is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the swisher-smoker##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
10. the person who likes azure is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
11. the fan of house is in the middle##1
12. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |     3      |     4     |       5       |
| Music-Genre         | classical  | ambient  | house    | rock | metal |
| Color   | orange        | chestnut  | azure | fuchsia      | coral        |
| Cigar   | alhambra       | swisher  | bongani   | prince | siglo     |
| Sport         | weightlifting | lacrosse | ice-hockey | climbing  | biathlon      |

