.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-7::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, banana, cherry, lettuce, raspberry
5 different pets are kept: goldfish, turtle, guinea-pig, hedgehog, rat
City: paris, san-francisco, hannover, berlin, miami
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, cola, tea, soy-milk
 1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 2. the person drinking cola is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 3. the person eating raspberry is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is the person traveling to paris##1
 5. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1
 6. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person traveling to hannover is in the middle##1
 8. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
10. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating cherry##1
12. the person drinking tea is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
13. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |     5     |
| Food          | cherry     | lettuce  | raspberry | banana     | artichoke |
| Pet           | goldfish   | turtle | rat     | guinea-pig | hedgehog |
| City   | paris | san-francisco  | hannover     | berlin   | miami    |
| Beverage     | iced-tea       | tea     | soy-milk     | cola      | fanta  |

