 8. the person who likes blue is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 9. the german is the person who likes yellow##1
10. the turkish is in the middle##1
11. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the turkish##1
12. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing domino##1
13. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
