.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-9::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice, tea, water
House: tower, futuristic, modern, farmhouse, colonial
There 5 different types of food: cucumber, lime, nectarine, grapefruit, pineapple
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, montecristo, davidoff, vegafina, dunhill
 1. the person eating pineapple is the modern house##1
 2. the futuristic house is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
 4. the colonial house is the chaman-smoker##1
 5. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 6. the chaman-smoker is the person eating lime##1
 7. the person drinking water is the person eating lime##1
 8. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 9. the colonial house is on the far left##1
10. the davidoff-smoker is the person drinking juice##1
11. the farmhouse house is the person eating nectarine##1
12. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the colonial house##1
13. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
14. the person drinking tea is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |      4       |     5      |
| Beverage      | water       | iced-tea   | tea        | 7up          | juice      |
| House         | colonial | futuristic | modern  | farmhouse | tower |
| Food   | lime  | cucumber    | pineapple       | nectarine         | grapefruit        |
| Cigar     | chaman    | vegafina    | dunhill | montecristo         | davidoff  |

