.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daisy, tulip, marigold, iris, rose
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, martial-arts, romance, scientific, western
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skiing, cricket, climbing, parkour, cycling
There are 5 different nationalities: russian, japanese, italian, canadian, indonesian
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 2. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1
 3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 4. the japanese is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the indonesian##1
 6. the italian is on the right of the japanese##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the russian##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 9. the indonesian is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
10. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
11. the canadian is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
12. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is parkour##1
13. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Flower      | daisy      | tulip       | rose         | iris  | marigold |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | scientific | martial-arts | crime  | western  |
| Sport   | parkour    | cricket    | skiing        | cycling | climbing     |
| Nationality           | japanese | italian      | russian       | canadian   | indonesian   |

