.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, davidoff, cain, bolivar, chaman
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, folk, gospel, jazz
There 5 different types of food: lettuce, carrot, pumpkin, kiwi, grapes
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: zinnia, daffodil, tulip, daisy, iris
 1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 2. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 3. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 4. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 7. the davidoff-smoker is the person who growszinnia##1
 8. the cain-smoker is the fan of country##1
 9. the person eating carrot is in the middle##1
10. the person eating lettuce is the fan of jazz##1
11. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
12. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
13. the bolivar-smoker is the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| Cigar   | davidoff      | bolivar | cain  | chaman    | tiparillo |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | jazz     | country | blues      | folk      |
| Food           | pumpkin       | lettuce     | carrot     | grapes     | kiwi   |
| Flower         | zinnia | daisy | daffodil  | iris | tulip   |

