.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, lemonade, milk, tea
There are 5 different nationalities: colombian, french, turkish, mexican, british
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skateboarding, sailing, ice-hockey, rugby, basketball
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: iris, daffodil, bellflower, poppy, sunflower
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 2. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 3. the british is the person who growsiris##1
 4. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growsdaffodil is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the french##1
 8. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 9. the person who growsiris is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
11. the colombian is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
12. the turkish is the person drinking tea##1
13. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
