.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
5 different pets are kept: snake, goat, fish, bird, dog
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, orchid, poppy, iris, aconite
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, davidoff, havana, prince, chaman
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter, snowmobile, train, tram
 1. the owner of the fish is in the middle##1
 2. the person who growsiris is the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 4. the person who growsbegonia is the chaman-smoker##1
 5. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 7. the person who growspoppy is the davidoff-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
10. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
11. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
12. the person who growsaconite is in the middle##1
13. the aristoff-smoker is the owner of the bird##1
14. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Pet      | goat | bird   | fish    | snake       | dog |
| Flower   | poppy           | orchid   | aconite   | iris       | begonia  |
| Cigar   | davidoff       | aristoff | havana | prince     | chaman   |
| Transport     | snowmobile    | scooter   | train   | helicopter | tram   |

 